<span id="freeTextContainer1757070014087329324">An incredibly detailed and sometimes very hard to push through read. It is rewarding if you have patience with it, and I imagine it feels much like an encyclopedia to someone who is more familiar with the subject. Would recommend to any proper history nerd. </span>

